==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unchristianize
<hw>Un*chris"tian*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>Christianize</ets>.]</ety> <def>To turn from
the Christian faith; to cause to abandon the belief and profession of
Christianity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unchristianly</ent>⟦br⟧
